cdata.name: GiftNet
cdata.desc: GiftNet is an ecosystem built on top of blockchain technology with the intent of providing a secure, anonymous marketplace in which free market economics prevail. GirftNet allows their users to encrypt their giftcard's verification code and only release the code once the desired clause has been met. GiftNet's native currency, GIFT is based on the x13 algorithm and uses a PoW protocol.
